node.text: Love this video the #AustraliaZoo team put together of the crocs swimming underwater. Steve and Terri designed the Crocoseum with clear water so everyone who visits can see how crocs behave in the wild and learn how to live alongside them. Honored to be part of this incredible work. Also enjoy seeing just how excited the crocs get for a feed! It’s so important that we protect these apex predators.
